                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9826" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1487</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1404 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重塑绿色钢铁：宝钢股份的碳资产管理之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Reinventing Green steel: Baosteel&#39;s path to carbon asset management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">林红珍，张子怡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宝山钢铁股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">25 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宝钢股份；碳资产管理；碳盘查；碳交易；全生命周期理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Baosteel; A &quot;two-carbon&quot; target; Full life cycle carbon asset management; Smart Carbon Data Platformmanagement</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在全球碳中和趋势及国内“双碳”政策驱动下，越来越多的钢铁企业意识到碳资产管理对提升竞争力、履行社会责任的关键作用。本案例聚焦钢铁行业巨头宝钢股份，描述其如何突破钢铁行业碳资产管理难点痛点，积极构建全生命周期碳资产管理体系的过程。宝钢股份通过战略布局，将碳资产管理理念融入企业发展核心，从碳盘查、碳预算、碳交易、碳技术、碳披露五个维度协同发力，全面提升碳资产管理效能，并积极参与国际碳市场规则制定，彰显绿色钢铁领航者之姿。2024年度的《中国上市公司双碳领导力排行榜》，宝钢股份再次位列第一。本案例可应用于管理会计课程教学，有助于学生理解全生命周期碳资产管理实践及其在推动企业可持续发展和实现“双碳”目标中的关键价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Under the global trend of carbon neutrality and the domestic &quot;dual carbon&quot; policy, an increasing number of steel enterprises have realized the crucial role of carbon asset management in enhancing competitiveness and fulfilling social responsibilities. This case focuses on Baosteel Co., Ltd., a leading player in the steel industry, and describes its process of breaking through the difficulties and pain points in carbon asset management in the steel industry and actively building a full life cycle carbon asset management system. Baosteel Co., Ltd. has integrated the concept of carbon asset management into the core of its development through strategic planning, and has made concerted efforts from five dimensions: carbon inventory, carbon budget, carbon trading, carbon technology, and carbon disclosure to comprehensively enhance the efficiency of carbon asset management. It has also actively participated in the formulation of international carbon market rules, demonstrating the posture of a leader in green steel. In the 2024 &quot;China Listed Companies&#39; Dual Carbon Leadership Ranking&quot;, Baosteel Co., Ltd. once again ranked first. This case can be applied in management accounting course teaching, helping students understand the practice of full life cycle carbon asset management and its key value in promoting sustainable development and achieving the &quot;dual carbon&quot; goals.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">碳盘查；碳预算；碳交易；碳披露；碳资产管理全生命周期理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
